with base    gcr gedit gpgme libnotify libsecret
with also    --disable-gpg-check
with role    security/encryption
with trait   x11 gnome
with source    stable $GNOME_URL sources/seahorse/${VERSION:0:3}/seahorse-$VERSION.tar.xz
with source  unstable $GNOME_URL sources/seahorse/${VERSION:0:3}/seahorse-$VERSION.tar.xz
with info    home http://seahorse.sourceforge.net
with info    cite 'GNOME front end for GnuPG
seahorse is a tool for secure communications and data storage.
Data encryption, digital signature creation, and key management
can all be performed through a GNOME-driven GUI.'
